<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ແກ້ໄຂລົດ (แก้ไขรถ / 編輯汽車)</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Phetsarath+OT:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-black">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/admin-secret/dashboard">ແອັດມິນ (แอดมิน / 管理員)</a>
            <div class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/admin-secret/manage-car">ຈັດການລົດ (จัดการรถ / 管理汽車)</a>
                <a class="nav-link" href="/admin-secret/manage-sell-requests">ຈັດການຄຳຂໍຂາຍ (จัดการคำขอขาย / 管理銷售請求)</a>
                <a class="nav-link" href="/admin-secret/logout">ອອກຈາກລະບົບ (ออกจากระบบ / 登出)</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-4">
        <h2 class="text-center">ແກ້ໄຂລົດ (แก้ไขรถ / 編輯汽車)</h2>
        <form action="/admin-secret/edit-car/<%- car._id %>?_method=PUT" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="brand" class="form-label">ຍີ່ຫໍ້ (ยี่ห้อ / 品牌)</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="brand" name="brand" value="<%- car.brand %>" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="model" class="form-label">ຮຸ່ນ (รุ่น / 型號)</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="model" name="model" value="<%- car.model %>" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="year" class="form-label">ປີ (ปี / 年份)</label>
                <input type="number" class="form-control" id="year" name="year" value="<%- car.year %>" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="price" class="form-label">ລາຄາ (ราคา / 價格)</label>
                <input type="number" class="form-control" id="price" name="price" value="<%- car.price %>" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="color" class="form-label">ສີ (สี / 顏色)</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="color" name="color" value="<%- car.color %>" required>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="location" class="form-label">ສະຖານທີ່ (สถานที่ / 地點)</label>
                <select class="form-control" id="location" name="location" required>
                    <% provinces.forEach(province => { %>
                        <option value="<%- province %>" <%- car.location === province ? 'selected' : '' %>><%- province %></option>
                    <% }) %>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="images" class="form-label">ຮູບພາບລົດ (รูปภาพรถ / 汽車圖片)</label>
                <input type="file" class="form-control" id="images" name="images" multiple accept="image/*">
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 form-check">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="isPremium" name="isPremium" <%- car.isPremium ? 'checked' : '' %>>
                <label class="form-check-label" for="isPremium">ລົດພຣີມຽມ (รถพรีเมียม / 高級汽車)</label>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">ບັນທຶກການປ່ຽນແປງ (บันทึกการเปลี่ยนแปลง / 保存更改)</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer bg-black text-gold mt-4">
        <div class="container py-4">
            <p class="text-center">© 2025 Used Car Sales. ສະຫງວນລິຂະສິດ (สงวนลิขสิทธิ์ / 版權所有)</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>